Name: Voxel Race
About the game: Climb aboard your vehicle and become the master of the track! Choose your car and customize it! Versus AI or your friends! Play on the controller or keyboard! In Voxel Race you will have the choice between two game modes: Free mode where you can explore the city at your leisure and race mode where your goal is to make the best time against the clock! Features: ■ Nice cubic decorations! ■ Race against the clock! ■ A great map explorable! ■ Partial joystick support! ■ Customization system! ■ Day / night system! ■ Good music!
